        "data": {
          "title": "The Bedroom",
          "content": "The room looks like every computer room you ever knew and none of them exactly.\n\nA rolling chair. A tower PC. Burned CDs stacked in a spindle. A printer with no paper. A shelf of blank VHS tapes labeled in someone else’s handwriting.\n\nOn the wall are framed screenshots of dead websites: GeoCities pages, vanished forums, glitter graphics, abandoned blogs, guestbooks full of ghosts.\n\nThe door has no knob.\n\nThe monitor flashes again.\n\nPLEASE COMPLETE INTAKE.",
